.TH "NAVIGATOR.PRODUCTSUB" "3JS" "August 25, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Navigator.productSub \- Navigator: productSub property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]Navigator.productSub\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property that
returns either the string \(lq20030107\(rq, or the string
\(lq20100101\(rq.
.SH VALUE
Either \(lq20030107\(rq, or \(lq20100101\(rq.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP
.EX
document.body.textContent = \(gaproductSub: ${navigator.productSub}\(ga;
.EE
.SH NOTES
On IE, this property returns undefined.
.PP
On Apple Safari and Google Chrome this property always returns
\f[CR]20030107\f[R].
.PP
On Firefox, this property always returns \f[CR]20100101\f[R].
